    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="letter">
                <pb n="1" xml:id="p.1"/>
                <div type="writingSession" n="1" hand="#pers.2098">
                    <opener>
                        <note place="mTop">
                            <hi rendition="#uu">
                                <persName key="pers.2098">LENGLIE</persName>
                            </hi>
                        </note>
                        <dateline rendition="#r">
                            <date when="1947-07-22">JUly 22, 1947</date>
                        </dateline>
                        <address>
                            <addrLine rendition="#r">
                                <placeName key="place.15.13.1">341 W. Hillcrest</placeName>
                            </addrLine>
                            <addrLine rendition="#r">Monrovia, Calif.</addrLine>
                        </address>
                        <address>
                            <addrLine>
                                <orgName key="org.1">Universal Edition</orgName>
                            </addrLine>
                            <addrLine>
                                <placeName key="place.9.11">Vienna, Austria</placeName>
                            </addrLine>
                        </address>
                    </opener>
                    <salute>Dear Sir:</salute>
                    <p> I would like to receive the following works of <persName key="pers.3263">Arnold
                        Schoenberg</persName>: <table rows="4" cols="5">
                            <row>
                                <cell>Op. 30</cell>
                                <cell>
                                    <bibl sameAs="werke.63">Quartett III</bibl>
                                </cell>
                                <cell>no. 8927</cell>
                                <cell>(catalogue price</cell>
                                <cell>$1.25)</cell>
                            </row>
                            <row>
                                <cell>Op. 9</cell>
                                <cell>
                                    <bibl sameAs="werke.2">Chamber Symphony</bibl>
                                </cell>
                                <cell>no. 7147</cell>
                                <cell>
                                    <ellipsis>
                                        <metamark function="ellipsis">〃</metamark>
                                        <supplied>(catalogue</supplied>
                                    </ellipsis>
                                    <ellipsis>
                                        <metamark function="ellipsis">〃</metamark>
                                        <supplied>price</supplied>
                                    </ellipsis>
                                </cell>
                                <cell>$2.00)</cell>
                            </row>
                            <row>
                                <cell>Op. 21</cell>
                                <cell>
                                    <bibl sameAs="werke.54">Pierrot lunaire</bibl>
                                </cell>
                                <cell>no. 5336</cell>
                                <cell>
                                    <ellipsis>
                                        <metamark function="ellipsis">〃</metamark>
                                        <supplied>(catalogue</supplied>
                                    </ellipsis>
                                    <ellipsis>
                                        <metamark function="ellipsis">〃</metamark>
                                        <supplied>price</supplied>
                                    </ellipsis>
                                </cell>
                                <cell>$2.00)</cell>
                            </row>
                            <row>
                                <cell/>
                                <cell>
                                    <bibl sameAs="schriften.1">Harmonielehre</bibl>
                                </cell>
                                <cell>no. <hi rendition="#circle">3370</hi>
                                </cell>
                                <cell>
                                    <ellipsis>
                                        <metamark function="ellipsis">〃</metamark>
                                        <supplied>(catalogue</supplied>
                                    </ellipsis>
                                    <ellipsis>
                                        <metamark function="ellipsis">〃</metamark>
                                        <supplied>price</supplied>
                                    </ellipsis>
                                </cell>
                                <cell>$6.00)</cell>
                            </row>
                        </table> I would like the following analyses of his works: <table rows="2" cols="3">
                            <row>
                                <cell>no. 5275</cell>
                                <cell>– $ .50</cell>
                            </row>
                            <row>
                                <cell>no. 6368</cell>
                                <cell>– $ .50</cell>
                            </row>
                        </table>Mr. <persName key="pers.3263">Schoenberg</persName> suggests that you send
                    them to me at your lowest <lb/>rates. I am a student of Mr. <persName key="pers.3263">Schoenberg</persName>, and need these works to write <lb/>a
                    book about his music. You can send <choice>
                            <sic>send</sic>
                            <corr type="deleted"/>
                        </choice> the music to me at the <lb/>following address: Mr. <persName key="pers.2098">Warren Langlie</persName>
                        <lb/>
                        <seg rendition="#c">c/o <persName key="pers.3263">Arnold Schoenberg</persName>
                            <lb/>
                            <placeName key="place.15.7.3.1">116 N. Rockingham</placeName>
                            <lb/>Brentwood Hills <lb/>W. Los Angeles <lb/>Calif. <lb/>USA</seg>
                    </p>
                    <p> I would like also the <persName key="pers.543">Brahms</persName>
                        <bibl sameAs="werke.155">folksong arrangements</bibl>. I do not find <lb/>them
                    listed in the catalogue I have, so I do not know the number, but <lb/>I am sure
                    you publish them.. </p>
                    <p>I send you $ 15.00,
                        and after I <lb/>receive your statement I will send you more if <lb/>this is
                        not enough, and will order other music.
                        <note place="right" hand="#addressee">I/48 erl: <lb/>
                            <gap reason="illegible" unit="chars" quantity="4"/>
                        </note>
                    </p>
                    <closer rendition="#r">
                        <salute>Yours truly,</salute>
                        <lb/>
                        <signed>
                            <persName key="pers.2098">W. Langlie</persName>
                        </signed>
                    </closer>
                </div>
                <div type="writingSession" n="2" hand="#pers.3263">
                    <salute>Dear Mr. <persName key="pers.3204">Schlee</persName>,</salute>
                    <p rendition="#inline">
                    I suggest to give the music
                    <lb/>to Mr <persName key="pers.2098">Langlie</persName> at my own rates.
                </p>
                    <p> Did you also send the parts of my <lb/>
                        <bibl sameAs="werke.59">Wind-Quintet</bibl>
                        <seg type="comment"><orig>to Mr <persName key="pers.2022"
                                >Krasner</persName>, or to Mr <lb/>
                                <persName key="pers.2392">Mikropolus</persName></orig><note
                                xml:id="namw_lsd_ncc" resp="#pkehrer">In Louis Krasner an Arnold
                                Schönberg, 21. Juni 1947 (<ref
                                    target="https://repo.schoenberg.at/urn:nbn:at:at-asc-B134888"
                                    >ASCC 13488</ref>), bittet <persName key="pers.2022"
                                    >Krasner</persName> um ein Material des Quintetts für eine
                                Aufführung unter der Leitung von Dimitri <persName key="pers.2392"
                                    >Mitropoulos</persName></note></seg>?
                        If not so send, please, a set <lb/>to me directly. </p>
                    <closer>
                        <salute rendition="#c">Cordially yours</salute>
                        <lb/>
                        <signed rendition="#r">
                            <persName key="pers.3263">Arnold Schönberg</persName>
                        </signed>
                    </closer>
                    <postscript>
                        <p>Thank you for your <seg type="comment"><orig>news about <lb/>the <bibl
                                        sameAs="werke.54">Pierrot</bibl>-performances</orig><note
                                    xml:id="ndlz_2b2_ncc" resp="#pkehrer">Alfred Schlee an Arnold
                                    Schönberg, 13. Mai 1947 (<ref
                                        target="https://repo.schoenberg.at/urn:nbn:at:at-asc-B177367"
                                        >ASCC 17736</ref>)</note></seg>. Can you <lb/>send me the
                                <seg type="comment"><orig>programs</orig><note xml:id="nufn_dg2_ncc"
                                    resp="#pkehrer">Exemplar aus dem Schönberg-Nachlass (<ref
                                        target="https://archive.schoenberg.at/resources/pages/view.php?ref=5788&amp;search=pierrot%2C+basicyear%3A1947&amp;offset=0&amp;order_by=relevance&amp;sort=DESC&amp;archive=&amp;k=&amp;">CP5788</ref>)</note></seg>?</p>
                        <signed rendition="#c">
                            <persName key="pers.3263">Sch</persName>
                        </signed>
                    </postscript>
                </div>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
